---
import ClerriLayout from '../../layouts/ClerriLayout.astro';
---
<ClerriLayout title="Patient Directory" section="directory">

<div class="page-head">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">08 · Consumer Acquisition</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">The single <em>highest-ROI</em> competitive move.</h1>
  <p class="page-sub">Jim explicitly liked this concept. Research validates it: practice density is a marketing weapon competitors can't replicate, and BoomCloud's "Patient Marketplace" — the supposed moat — is a paper tiger.</p>
</div>

<div class="page-body">

  <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-progress-fill="directory"></div></div>
  <p class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)">Progress: <span data-progress-here="directory">0 / 0</span></p>

  <div class="callout zest-hi">
    <div class="lbl">The Asymmetry</div>
    <p>Clerri has <strong>5,000+ practices</strong>. BoomCloud's ThePatientMarketplace.com gets <strong>2,400 visits/month with 79.6% bounce rate</strong>, propped up by paid display ads. The "national patient directory" narrative is being claimed without the asset. Clerri's structural scale + modest investment dwarfs them within 6 months and neutralizes BoomCloud's only true differentiator.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Strategic rationale</h2>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Why this matters</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.9rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Captures bottom-of-funnel patient demand (72M+ uninsured)</li>
        <li>Direct revenue: every enrollment is recurring (Bucket 02)</li>
        <li>Defensible: practice density makes directory genuinely useful</li>
        <li>Practice value: tangible patient acquisition no competitor offers</li>
        <li>Category narrative: positions Clerri as connector</li>
        <li>Two-tier monetization: free baseline, paid premium</li>
        <li>Designed for horizontal expansion (DPC, vision, med spa)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h4>Build components</h4>
      <ul style="font-size:0.9rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Geographic search + plan filtering + practice profiles</li>
        <li>Base practice listings (location, contact, plans, reviews)</li>
        <li>Premium tier (featured placement, lead capture, analytics)</li>
        <li>Local SEO foundation (city-level pages at scale via AI)</li>
        <li>PMS integration for live availability</li>
        <li>Sunbit financing integration on listing pages</li>
        <li>Compliance review (DMPO, state-specific)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Phased rollout hypothesis</h2>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card" style="border-color:var(--clerri-green)">
      <div class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--clerri-green);letter-spacing:0.1em">PHASE 1 · MONTHS 1-3</div>
      <h3 style="margin:0.5rem 0">Validate</h3>
      <ul style="font-size:0.875rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Scope with product/eng</li>
        <li>Decide build vs partner (NexHealth integration could accelerate)</li>
        <li>BoomCloud Marketplace teardown — what works, what doesn't</li>
        <li>Compliance pre-clearance (DMPO, state-specific)</li>
        <li>Pilot landing page in 5 metros to measure demand</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--clerri-green);letter-spacing:0.1em">PHASE 2 · MONTHS 4-6</div>
      <h3 style="margin:0.5rem 0">Build MVP</h3>
      <ul style="font-size:0.875rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Practice profiles + basic search</li>
        <li>Free tier across all practices (default-on)</li>
        <li>City-page SEO scaffolding via AI (workflow C)</li>
        <li>Soft launch in 3-5 metros with paid geo support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--clerri-green);letter-spacing:0.1em">PHASE 3 · MONTHS 7-9</div>
      <h3 style="margin:0.5rem 0">Monetize</h3>
      <ul style="font-size:0.875rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Premium tier features (featured placement, lead capture, analytics)</li>
        <li>Sunbit financing integration on practice pages</li>
        <li>Lead routing economics analysis</li>
        <li>Practice success measurement framework</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="border-color:var(--clerri-green)">
      <div class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--clerri-green);letter-spacing:0.1em">PHASE 4 · MONTHS 10-12+</div>
      <h3 style="margin:0.5rem 0">Scale</h3>
      <ul style="font-size:0.875rem;padding-left:1rem">
        <li>Scale local SEO across all 5,000+ practice locations</li>
        <li>Paid acquisition where unit economics work</li>
        <li>Integrate employer channel (ICHRA + LSA reimbursement)</li>
        <li>Open architecture for adjacent specialties (horizontal thesis)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Tasks</h2>
  <div data-section="directory">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="dir-01-teardown" data-section="directory" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Personally teardown BoomCloud's ThePatientMarketplace — document everything</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="dir-02-product-scope" data-section="directory" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Phase 1: scoping meeting with product + eng — build vs partner decision</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="dir-03-nexhealth" data-section="directory" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Evaluate NexHealth (400+ integrations) as build-acceleration partner</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="dir-04-compliance" data-section="directory" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Compliance pre-clearance — DMPO + state-specific for consumer-facing directory</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="dir-05-pilot-metros" data-section="directory" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Pilot landing page in 5 high-density Clerri metros to measure consumer demand</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="dir-06-jim-greenlight" data-section="directory" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Greenlight conversation with Jim — present economic model + phased commit</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <div class="note-block">
    <div class="note-label">Directory strategy notes <span class="note-saved">✓ saved</span></div>
    <textarea data-note="directory-notes" placeholder="Build vs partner decision rationale, pilot results, compliance constraints, partner conversations..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="topic-foot">
    <a href="/clerri/aeo-seo"><span class="dir">← Prev</span><span class="name">07 · AEO / SEO / SEM</span></a>
    <a href="/clerri/ai-stack"><span class="dir">Next →</span><span class="name">09 · AI Marketing Stack</span></a>
  </div>

</div>
</ClerriLayout>
